java.lang.Cloneable
public class BetweenFE
extends SegmentationFE

The BetweenFE evaluates its successor in the chain whenever the input feature is in the range min to max, inclusive.

Min or max may be null, and then equal -infinity to infinity

If the inputFeature is null the test never succeeds, regardless of min/max.
